title: The Jam-Super Cool Color Injected...One-Shot-Bernie Mireault
description:
This is it...the last of THE JAM issues. there are a couple of team-up issues with Allred's Madman which are already available in other torrents.

Bernie Mireault's 'Jammer' is one of the most creative and engaging takes on life and super-heroics in years. It's a refreshing combination of adventure and pathos that is neither cliche nor a spoof. The Jam is an original.

ENJOY
